# Linear KPI Runner

## What it does
- Generates pod-wise cycle KPI report
- Tracks spillover using SQLite state
- Produces CSV and Markdown outputs in out/

## Prerequisites
- Node.js 20+

## Install
npm install

## Run
LINEAR_API_KEY="YOUR_KEY" node scripts/runWeeklyKpi.js

## Config files
- config/pods.json
- config/cycle_calendar.json
- config/label_ids.json
- config/linear_ids.json

## Outputs
- out/pod_cycle_kpi.csv
- out/pod_feature_movement.csv
- out/kpi_weekly_report.md

